<template>
  <v-container
    fill-height
    fluid
    grid-list-xl>
    <v-layout
      justify-center
      wrap
    >
      <v-flex
        xs12
        md8
      >
        <material-card
          color="green"
          title="Login"
        >
          <v-form>
            <v-container py-0>
              <v-layout wrap>

                <v-flex
                  xs12
                  md4
                >
                  <v-text-field
                    class="purple-input"
                    label="User Name"
                  />
                </v-flex>
                <v-flex
                  xs12
                  text-xs-right
                >
                  <v-btn
                    class="mx-0 font-weight-light"
                    color="success"
                  >
                   Register
                  </v-btn>
                </v-flex>
              </v-layout>
            </v-container>
          </v-form>
        </material-card>
      </v-flex>
      <v-flex
        xs12
        md4
      >
      </v-flex>
    </v-layout>
  </v-container>
</template>

<script>
var saved = false;
export default {
  //
  data(){
    return {
      saved
    }
  },

  methods:{
    praise(){
      if(this.saved){
        this.saved = false;
      }
      else{
        this.saved = true;
      }
    }
  }
}
</script>
